{"tid":1520970,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【哎喲喲】G7重申《中英聯合聲明》有效　中國「發爛渣」","createTime":"2019-08-31T04:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T21:34:53.000Z","uid":53003,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4989fc0f11b0db00428a3a4ce37e37f62857ad30","tid":1520970,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:16:47.000Z","msg":"本周G7七大工業國召開峰會，在事前外界完全沒有準備之下，與會領袖突然提及香港問題，重申《中英聯合聲明》有效及重要，以及呼籲各方避免暴力。這是各民主國家首次集體強調「聯合聲明」的重要性，完全是針對中國近年不斷聲稱「聯合聲明」是「歷史文件」，或已不再有效，或已「過時無效」等的說法作出反擊，可說是中國外交上的大挫敗。<br />\n<br />\n七國集團的聲明當中，只提及了貿易問題、伊朗、利比亞以及俄羅斯侵佔克里米亞的烏克蘭問題，因此香港突然與這些戰亂地區相提並論，說明了目前中國在香港種種挑戰「聯合聲明」的行為，已為民主國家所不容與質疑。事實上「聯合聲明」就是一條國際條約，如果中國可以簽完就不信守，那麼又有誰會相信中國再簽的任何協議？<br />\n<br />\n如果美國同樣以「歷史文件」來定義中美建交的三個聯合公布，即否認「一個中國」，然後承認台灣為國家，中國忍受得了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n中共這種橫蠻無理的手段，正說明了中國對各民主國家形成的挑戰，如今已上升到不止是引起英國或美國所質疑的問題，而是連英國、加拿大、法國、德國、義大利、日本與美國，所共同質疑的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（以上評論純屬主持與嘉賓個人觀點，並不代表本台立場。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/talkshows/vharbor/lktk1-08302019132906.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Ftalkshows%2Fvharbor%2Flktk1-08302019132906.html&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2YoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=c69b96b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/talkshows/vharbor/lktk1-08302019132906.html</a>"},{"pid":"bf04085b486a30936aec79590d6472c5fdbbd02a","tid":1520970,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 港島  最後召集 </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 民陣呼籲  民主之光 </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.01 機場  13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.02 全港三罷 </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"11372e5e034440a130d544aeabaca5d6776714c9","tid":1520970,"uid":211194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"好撚柒啊媽咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e680416be3c5384fdf2ff8b2258974af21374828","tid":1520970,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:41:56.000Z","msg":"仲有一萬億債券呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自古以來回力鏢"},{"pid":"97040b8900c0b9975ad90ec61521f7bc84ff0586","tid":1520970,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"柒出國際"},{"pid":"b526b0773a219f5983d39a4279c5020c974f8e96","tid":1520970,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:34:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【國際路線】全世界印同舉依款標語</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifcqnMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifcqnMz.png&h=19bda72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/taez0yf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftaez0yf.png&h=868ecca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttTpDjV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttTpDjV.png&h=ada7f3ab&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}